他說耶穌說

29
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:18,560
I am coming

30
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:20,680
I am coming

31
00:01:20,680 --> 00:01:22,640
I am coming

32
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:23,840
講著講著

33
